OL,5, Conspiracy theorist Alex Jones has been
OL,6, ordered to pay an extra $473m (#405m)  
OL,7, for falsely claiming the Sandy Hook    
OL,8, school shooting was a hoax.            
OL,10,FThe Connecticut judge's order brings to
OL,11,F$1.44bn the total amount Jones has to  
OL,12,Fpay following the defamation trial.    
OL,14,FPlaintiffs had asked for extra damages,
OL,15,Fciting Jones's "utter lack of          
OL,16,Frepentance" and "historic" wrongdoing. 
OL,18,FJones now admits the attack in which 20
OL,19,Fchildren and six adults were killed on 
OL,20,F14 December 2012 was "100% real".      
